I hope this boat is unbreakable.. can we survive the Dangie waters or will we end up underwater.. Winner gets to press the golden mystery button which has a hidden secret punishment for the loser. It's very satisfying seeing Chris and Jeff get absolutely covered in some of the nastiest punishments YouTube has seen!  Being trapped on this boat is not where you want to be!
